{"tid":349134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：一地兩檢是「必須做、並非選擇」","createTime":"2017-08-06T10:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T09:30:01.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1cbe363205236d77db3ef7d4a89302731a2c19","tid":349134,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"署理行政長官張建宗表示，一地兩檢方案是與內地當局審視後，唯一可行的方案，「是必須做，並非選擇」，但他表示，明白社會希望了解多點，政府同意要做好解說及溝通，會多聽意見，完善實際操作機制；希望社會未來可以更務實看待問題，研究如何完善一地兩檢安排。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗表示，過去10日，政府已經很清楚地解釋，為何有需要落實一地兩檢，因有關方案長遠在操作及經濟效益等方面，都是唯一可行方案，故應該向前推進。他認為，政府應繼續解說，加強市民對方案的理解，釋除憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，政府具有誠意，港鐵公司亦有安排議員作實地考察，了解運作，泛民議員卻杯葛不出席；但政府會繼續聆聽意見，亦樂意溝通。"},{"pid":"3f1dfadcee7f2dac53afb6beac920b2b998d1a6a","tid":349134,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d807ace921d3995597c96d953c363bb7cc18964","tid":349134,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/bugloved/110052128458_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fbugloved%2F110052128458_n.jpg&h=a86ed9a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ea0070452d28593a858350f9313da5adf0bc74b","tid":349134,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食屎啦賣港"},{"pid":"459952099410a6e1d8410b5d4eab95ef85fe19e4","tid":349134,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bb4712e61508183b27f5f0d9181c696e0ea4fc","tid":349134,"uid":20816,"like